Message:
I have a question

We started to test new Ad: NB-Memo-Vid3-compl2b-Erin

On Saturday we received 47 clicks, 2.17$ per click and we have 2 sales + upsell, so 130$ so in profit... but clicks kind of too expensive...

So I changed the Ad Set settings from Max Conversions to CPA and and Sunday and today we received 415 clicks

really good price 15c per click, but absolutelly no action, no engagements, no purchases, seems like very low quality traffic...

this offer converts really good, and usually we get add order form impression every 15-20-30 clicks

but absolutelly nothing from 415 visitors, something does not seem right...

Could it be because of the Audience Network? Placements?

I see that there is option to turn off the Audience Network? is this a good idea? any suggestions? should we turn it off?

what would you recommend ?
